 HAVING a great-fitting kimono jacket in your wardrobe can help you create some great outfits. That is why Kimono jackets apart from blazers are the second pick for a wardrobe must. These are items you have that are not especially trendy and can be paired with lots of great stuff to create your own unique look. Kimono jackets are a great basis for a stylish outfit, especially a darker pair; you can dress them up or down.